To demonstrate the performance of a logistic regression by using
choosen database with python code.

CODE:


import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
def sigmoid(z):
    return 1 / (1 + np.exp( - z))
plt.plot(np.arange(-5, 5, 0.1), sigmoid(np.arange(-5, 5, 0.1)),color='pink')
plt.title('Visualization of the Sigmoid Function')
plt.show()
